<div id="howitworks">
    <h3>How it works</h3>
    <div id="stepOne" class="step fourcol">
        <h4>Log in</h4>
        You'll be asked to grant permission for boxsocial to access your Last.fm account.
    </div>
    <div id="stepTwo" class="step fourcol">
        <h4>Join a party</h4>
        Check that your host is scrobbling and find out their Last.fm username. Enter their username to join or create a new party.
    </div>
    <div id="stepThree" class="step fourcol last">
        <h4>That's it</h4>
        All of the tracks that your host plays will appear in your own Last.fm timeline. When you want to stop just click 'Leave Party'.
    </div>
</div>
